column3: Uff, very very nice video, no joke, so well told and very delicate.
Loved it.... Its a poetry to me.

As a Parisian rider, this video emphasis a phantasm about Paris. The reality is that Paris is small, the traffic over congestioned, the city polluted by traffic and it is getting worse every year. It is getting annoying to see again and again the city shown like a pleasant old city with a village atmosph√®re. it is not the reality, it is not Paris ! it is fairy  tales for that hipster/voutuber genra .
After all, a woman riding a bicycle is beautiful.
Beautiful video. Captures the love of cycling.
Brilliant - must do a ride out to Vetheuil next time in Paris.  Thanks for that.
The world needs more humans like this beautiful and perfect person.
Lovely. Make me wanna ride even though I've caught a bad cold...
Beautiful video, one of my favourite cities, and also one of my favourite video from the Rapha Ride series so far. I hope you let me know when you're doing Sydney next (as a Sydneysider!).
